# This is a mere example of how env variables are handled in local environments.  
# Do not commit real API keys to git.
#
# Groq:         https://console.groq.com/keys
# Ollama Cloud: https://ollama.com/settings/keys
# Reddit needs no key - it's read via public RSS feeds.
GROQ_API_KEY=
OLLAMA_API_KEY=

# --- Daily PDF digest -> Google Drive (one-time setup) ---
# 1. Google Cloud Console: enable the Drive API, create a service account,
#    add a JSON key, download it. Put that file's ABSOLUTE path below.
# 2. In Google Drive, create/pick a folder, share it with the service
#    account's email as Editor, and copy the folder id from the folder URL.
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_FILE=
GOOGLE_DRIVE_FOLDER_ID=
